OL,5, Former President Donald Trump must pay 
OL,6, nearly $355m (#281m) to New York state 
OL,7, for lying about the values of his      
OL,8, properties, a judge has ruled.         
OL,10,FJudge Arthur Engoron also banned him   
OL,11,Ffrom serving as a company director or  
OL,12,Ftaking out loans from banks in the     
OL,13,Fstate for three years.                 
OL,15,FThe New York real estate mogul escaped 
OL,16,Fhaving some of his companies dissolved,
OL,17,Fwhich could have meant bankruptcy.     
OL,19,FSpeaking from his Florida estate, Mr   
OL,20,FTrump said he would appeal the ruling. 
